@chatBase = http://localhost:8003/api/v1
@authToken = user_token_123

### Exportar chat completo como PDF — descarga chat_1.pdf
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/export/pdf/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Exportar chat completo como Markdown — descarga chat_1.md
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/export/markdown/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Exportar chat completo como JSON — descarga chat_1.json
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/export/json/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Exportar solo respuestas de IA como Markdown — descarga chat_1_ai.md
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/export/ai/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Exportar un mensaje individual como PDF — descarga message_55.pdf
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/1/messages/55/export/pdf/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
